{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013QVeYtrywwrC7SaJGE5pxL","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Harness Cost Report\n     2→\n     3→Total API-equivalent cost: $651.59\n     4→Total API calls: 4815\n     5→Average cost per story: $3.33 (155 stories)\n     6→\n     7→## Cost by Token Type\n     8→\n     9→| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n    10→|------|--------|------|------|---|\n    11→| Cache reads | 267,002,937 | $1.50/MTok | $400.50 | 61% |\n    12→| Cache writes | 7,989,210 | $18.75/MTok | $149.80 | 23% |\n    13→| Output | 1,348,067 | $75/MTok | $101.11 | 16% |\n    14→| Input | 12,173 | $15/MTok | $0.18 | 0% |\n    15→\n    16→## Cost by Phase\n    17→\n    18→| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n    19→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    20→| verify | 2888 | $364.99 | 56.0% |\n    21→| orchestrator | 546 | $119.75 | 18.4% |\n    22→| retro | 461 | $65.49 | 10.1% |\n    23→| create-story | 344 | $36.58 | 5.6% |\n    24→| code-review | 305 | $34.70 | 5.3% |\n    25→| dev-story | 271 | $30.07 | 4.6% |\n    26→\n    27→## Cost by Tool\n    28→\n    29→| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n    30→|------|-------|------|---|\n    31→| Bash | 2031 | $250.03 | 38.4% |\n    32→| Read | 941 | $125.53 | 19.3% |\n    33→| Edit | 620 | $79.60 | 12.2% |\n    34→| Agent | 433 | $57.03 | 8.8% |\n    35→| Skill | 131 | $47.85 | 7.3% |\n    36→| Grep | 301 | $35.25 | 5.4% |\n    37→| Write | 138 | $25.36 | 3.9% |\n    38→| TodoWrite | 105 | $14.40 | 2.2% |\n    39→| Glob | 85 | $13.21 | 2.0% |\n    40→| ToolSearch | 26 | $2.90 | 0.4% |\n    41→\n    42→## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n    43→\n    44→| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n    45→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    46→| unknown | 659 | $135.26 | 20.8% |\n    47→| 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile | 190 | $23.63 | 3.6% |\n    48→| 14-4-observability-backend-choice | 192 | $22.13 | 3.4% |\n    49→| 8-9-semgrep-rules-rust-observability | 121 | $17.10 | 2.6% |\n    50→| 8-2-expand-state-types-for-rust | 84 | $12.67 | 1.9% |\n    51→| 16-5-rewrite-harness-run-verification-dispatch | 106 | $11.22 | 1.7% |\n    52→| 9-5-multi-stack-docs-remaining-consumers | 84 | $11.07 | 1.7% |\n    53→| 11-2-sprint-status-yaml-derived-view | 74 | $10.80 | 1.7% |\n    54→| 11-1-unified-sprintstate-schema-versioning | 75 | $10.27 | 1.6% |\n    55→| 12-4-shared-test-utilities-fixtures | 85 | $9.98 | 1.5% |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_017LJ5i13zUB4Wpphd9vrz99","session_id":"2610e689-589b-4ec2-8784-d06d07275472","uuid":"7fd8c9b8-304f-4a58-a66c-23f76b39f43e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T15:05:41.225Z"}
