{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017LJ5i13zUB4Wpphd9vrz99","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Session 21 retrospective appended to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md`.\n\nKey points:\n- **Root cause identified**: `parseRalphMessage()` regex matches inside stream-json NDJSON lines, causing `handleAgentEvent()` to corrupt state via `updateStoryStatus()` which creates phantom entries for unknown keys\n- **Cost**: $651.59 total across 4,815 calls. Estimated $22-30 wasted on 12 state-corruption sessions\n- **Two critical fixes needed**: (1) skip regex matching on lines starting with `{`, (2) make `updateStoryStatus()` reject unknown keys\n- **7 action items** documented, with items 1-2 as the critical root cause fixes"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a9a8a087411422cc8 (use SendMessage with to: 'a9a8a087411422cc8' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 28553\ntool_uses: 10\nduration_ms: 81438</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2610e689-589b-4ec2-8784-d06d07275472","uuid":"4b184c35-881c-4024-be31-f1ce57c6d959","timestamp":"2026-03-27T15:06:52.565Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Run a session retrospective for the current sprint session. This is a research/writing task only — do NOT modify any code files.\n\nSprint status: _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/sprint-status.yaml\nSession issues log: _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md\nCost report: Run `codeharness stats --save` to get the cost report, then read `_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/cost-report.md`.\n\nContext for this session (Session 21):\n- All 74 stories were already done at session start\n- The session was spent investigating the ROOT CAUSE of a state corruption bug that has plagued 12+ previous sessions\n- Root cause found: `parseRalphMessage()` in `src/lib/agents/ralph.ts` matches `[SUCCESS] Story {key}: DONE` regex patterns WITHIN stream-json NDJSON lines. When claude session output contains tool results or text with these patterns, the regex matches inside the JSON envelope, and `handleAgentEvent()` calls `updateStoryStatus(key, 'review')`, resetting done stories to review or creating phantom entries.\n- Evidence: 3 phantom stories were created during this session: `16-5-xxx`, `16-5-foo`, `1-1-foo`\n- Fix needed: (1) Skip ralph pattern matching for lines starting with `{` (stream-json lines), (2) `updateStoryStatus()` should not create new story entries for unknown keys\n- Cleaned up phantom entries, restored 74/74 state\n\nProduce a retrospective covering:\n1. Session summary\n2. Issues analysis — the root cause finding is the main item\n3. Cost analysis from cost report\n4. What went well — finally found the root cause after 12 sessions of state fixes\n5. What went wrong — 12+ sessions wasted before root cause investigation\n6. Lessons learned\n7. Action items — the fix for parseRalphMessage is critical\n\nWrite to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md. If it already exists, append with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions. Do NOT run git commit. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","agentId":"a9a8a087411422cc8","agentType":"general-purpose","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Session 21 retrospective appended to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md`.\n\nKey points:\n- **Root cause identified**: `parseRalphMessage()` regex matches inside stream-json NDJSON lines, causing `handleAgentEvent()` to corrupt state via `updateStoryStatus()` which creates phantom entries for unknown keys\n- **Cost**: $651.59 total across 4,815 calls. Estimated $22-30 wasted on 12 state-corruption sessions\n- **Two critical fixes needed**: (1) skip regex matching on lines starting with `{`, (2) make `updateStoryStatus()` reject unknown keys\n- **7 action items** documented, with items 1-2 as the critical root cause fixes"}],"totalDurationMs":81438,"totalTokens":28553,"totalToolUseCount":10,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":348,"cache_read_input_tokens":28002,"output_tokens":202,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":348},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
